might make that happen.

280
00:13:42,875 --> 00:13:44,458
[NOZOMI] Ya think we
should pick a leader?

281
00:13:44,541 --> 00:13:45,708
[SAYAKA]
Yes.

282
00:13:45,791 --> 00:13:47,333
