what I already suspected.

411
00:19:05,375 --> 00:19:06,625
I knew you had a nice rack,

412
00:19:06,708 --> 00:19:08,375
but didn't know
how nice till today.

413
00:19:08,458 --> 00:19:09,166
[KAZANE gasps]

414
00:19:09,250 --> 00:19:10,875
Stop it! Don't be creepy!

415
00:19:10,958 --> 00:19:13,041
[NOZOMI] There's no need
for you to be embarrassed!

416
00:19:13,125 --> 00:19:15,416
So what cup size are you? A "D"?

417
00:19:15,500 --> 00:19:19,833
Not quite that big, huh?
Lemme guess, a "C"!

418
00:19:19,916 --> 00:19:22,208
Ah-ha! We have the
same cup size!

419
00:19:22,291 --> 00:19:23,208
But... I never.

420
00:19:23,291 --> 00:19:24,541
I know.

421
00:19:24,625 --> 00:19:26,333
Nozomin's having a
conversation with her ponytail!

422
00:19:26,416 --> 00:19:28,458
I don't understand why
Aoba would be embarrassed

423
00:19:28,541 --> 00:19:31,333
by her breasts when
they're a "C" cup.

424
00:19:31,416 --> 00:19:34,000
[HITOMI] I'd like to welcome
you to your first Land class.

425
00:19:34,083 --> 00:19:35,375
We're going to be
starting things off

426
00:19:35,458 --> 00:19:37,458
with a mock race
against the teachers.

427
00:19:37,541 --> 00:19:39,458
We'll be using a basic Land.

428
00:19:39,541 --> 00:19:42,208
Each team of four students
will compete with one teacher.

429
00:19:42,291 --> 00:19:44,833
Four against one, huh?
I like those odds.

430
00:19:44,916 --> 00:19:46,541
[HITOMI] We'll evaluate
your Keijo ability

431
00:19:46,625 --> 00:19:48,833
by going cheek-to-cheek
with you on the Land.

432
00:19:48,916 --> 00:19:50,250
Don't worry about
holding back.

433
00:19:50,333 --> 00:19:52,500
I want you to give me
everything you've got.

434
00:19:57,458 --> 00:19:58,833
[HITOMI yells]

435
00:20:01,666 --> 00:20:03,291
Ms. Hokuto's really strong!

436
00:20:03,375 --> 00:20:04,958
I still can't believe
they're gonna make us

437
00:20:05,041 --> 00:20:06,208
play against a teacher!

438
00:20:06,291 --> 00:20:08,666
If we gotta do it,
then we might as well win.

439
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:11,500
[NAGISA]
Okay. Up next is room 309.

440
00:20:11,583 --> 00:20:12,916
[ALL gasp]

441
00:20:15,791 --> 00:20:17,416
[NOZOMI]
Why'd we get the seal?

442
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:18,916
You know she can
hear you, right?

443
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:20,666
Ms. Ujibe may not look it now,

444
00:20:20,750 --> 00:20:23,041
but she used to be
quite the prize queen!

445
00:20:23,125 --> 00:20:24,541
[SAYAKA]
Nagisa Ujibe.

446
00:20:24,625 --> 00:20:27,208
She was a top player
in Keijo's early days.

447
00:20:27,291 --> 00:20:29,333
Her remarkable beauty
and her playful tactics

448
00:20:29,416 --> 00:20:33,250
earned her the nickname
the "Alluring Siren."

449
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:35,333
[grunts]

450
00:20:35,416 --> 00:20:36,583
[NOZOMI]
You're kidding.

451
00:20:36,666 --> 00:20:38,125
What're you mumbling
about over there?

452
00:20:38,208 --> 00:20:39,791
C'mon, let's get started!

453
00:20:39,875 --> 00:20:40,916
[GIRLS]
Yes, ma'am!

454
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,291
[NOZOMI]
Don't let her intimidate ya.

455
00:20:42,375 --> 00:20:44,166
We gotta stick to the plan!

456
00:20:45,791 --> 00:20:47,166
[NOZOMI]
I'll go first!

457
00:20:48,375 --> 00:20:50,000
Crap, she didn't even budge!

458
00:20:50,083 --> 00:20:50,916
Fine then!

459
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:52,375
Let's work together to show her

460
00:20:52,458 --> 00:20:55,125
