our team can be!

461
00:20:56,125 --> 00:20:58,583
Look! Nozomi's out on the land!

462
00:21:03,083 --> 00:21:04,000
[NAGISA]
Hm.

463
00:21:06,416 --> 00:21:07,416
[NAGISA]
